			#("anim_nonlinear_rotation_keys_may_a_tip", "Non-linear rotation keys may animate improperly in wc3 if they go beyond 90\\\\xC2\\\\xB0. This tool will apply fixes to those keys by creating a new key between them. Note that you may have to run the tool more than once in some weird occasions where you created rotations of over 180\\\\xC2\\\\xB0"),
			#("anim_automatically_create_attachmen_tip", "Automatically create Attachment Points for Bones that have known names."),
			#("anim_saves_parent_relationships_of_tip", "Saves parent relationships of selected objects and unlinks them from their parents\n\nSometimes you already got a bunch of meshes linked to some bones and suddenly you want to edit the bones. If you don't want to mess up the meshes, you must unlink them, do whatever you need, then relink. This tool saves the parents of the selected meshes, unlinks them and restores them when you want. Use this tool before converting bones from IK to FK, for instance."),
			#("anim_restores_previously_saved_pare_tip", "Restores previously saved parent relationships for selected objects\n\nSometimes you already got a bunch of meshes linked to some bones and suddenly you want to edit the bones. If you don't want to mess up the meshes, you must unlink them, do whatever you need, then relink. This tool saves the parents of the selected meshes, unlinks them and restores them when you want. Use this tool before converting bones from IK to FK, for instance."),
